    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "VTAL\n000000₴\nThis is\nthe airline\npride built",
      "CONTINENTAL\nthe proud bird\nwith the golden tail\nThe history of Continental\nAirlines dates back\nto 1934 -from the\ntime of the classic\nfour-passenger\nLockheed Vega right\nup to the introduction\nof our\nmagnificent 747, the Proud Bird of the Pacific,\nin June, 1970. We've come a long way...offering\nservice that continues to reflect the personal\nconcern our people have in their airline and in\nthe comfort of its passengers.\nYou're sure to feel this personal pride and\nthe difference it makes whenever and wherever\nyou travel on Continental Airlines. For this is\ntruly the airline that pride built.",
      "The Proud Bird with the Golden Tail\nCONTINENTAL\nONTINEI\n00\n0000000.\nAJ88 LITHO IN U.S.A."
    ],
